
Kubernetes Stack in Production:

1.  Infrastructure:

      a.Container Registry
      b.DNS
      c.Load Balancing
      d.IP Address
      e.IaC Setup

2.  Security:

      a.Secrect Mangement
          i.Vault
          ii.External Secret Synchronization
      b.Kubernetes RBAC

3.  AUTO:

    a. QAUTO/OIDC
    b. IAM
    c. Single SignOn

4.  Observability:

    a.Monitoring:
      i.Dashboards
      ii. Notifications.

    b.Logging
      i. Collections.
      ii. Indexes.
      iii. Tracing.


5.  Releases & Deployments:

    a. GitOps Platform.
    b. CI/CD.
    c. Rolling Deployments.
    d. Autotesting.

6.  Development:

    a. Deployment.
    b. Service.
    c. Ingress.
    d. Configuration.
      i. Configmaps.
      ii. Secretes
      iii. Liveness & Readiness probes.
